### 1. LOGIN - Get JWT Token
POST {{Courses_Management_System_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

### 2. GET All Students
GET {{Courses_Management_System_HostAddress}}/api/students
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. GET Student by ID
GET {{Courses_Management_System_HostAddress}}/api/students/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

